metadata.name: #1 AFRIAN GODDESS
metadata.description: I am a feminist, and what that means to me is much the same as the meaning of the fact that I am Black;"I need to see my own beauty and to continue to be reminded that I am enough, that I am worthy of love without effort, that I am beautiful, that the texture of my hair and that the shape of my curves, the size of my lips, the color of my skin, and the feelings that I have are all worthy.
